column2: select   s.specobjID, s.bestobjID, s.firstrelease, s.survey, s.sourcetype, s.class,   p.ra, p.raErr, p.dec, p.decErr, s.z, s.zErr,   p.modelMag_r, p.modelMag_i, p.modelMag_g,  p.psfMag_r, p.psfMag_i, p.psfMag_g,   p.petroMag_r, p.petroR5#_r into mydb.LRG from SpecObj as s   join PhotoObj as p on p.ObjID = s.bestobjID where   s.zwarning = #    and s.sourcetype = &&&
